Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1

Looks good Grzegorz but the music-cassandra image has some customization to create user/role like below.
Additionally, we need to run portal.cql file when Cassandra loads.


CREATE ROLE IF NOT EXISTS <CASSUSER> WITH PASSWORD = '<CASSPASS>' AND SUPERUSER = True AND LOGIN = True;
ALTER ROLE cassandra WITH PASSWORD = 'SomeLongRandomStringNoonewillthinkof';

We need to make sure this is happening once we start using the new image. Can you please provide your thoughts on this.
